snippet.title: Arcade Game: Yamato (1983 Sega)
snippet.description:
An shooting 'em up/gallery game.

Note: Used invincibility cheat after down to last life. Also use autofire and no delay between bullet reload cheat to speed up the levels. The game is endless.
